generating a translated URL in the second language, representing the first web page, based on the translated text in the second language;
storing the translated URL in the second language as being associated with the original URL; and
replacing the original URL with the translated URL wherever the original URL appears on a second web page in the first language that is being translated into the second language.
Item 61. The method of Item 60, wherein the human translation is aided by the machine translation.
